data.description: You deserve the best, and this home gives you a great piece of small town living to call home. The large living room welcomes you in, where you have updates solid surface flooring leading you into the great kitchen/dining room. New carpet and updates to the master bedroom and en suite give you comfortable place lay your head.  Teh split bedroom design give you two more bedrooms and full bathroom on the other side of the house.  Outside, the large generously sized backyard gives everyone a place to play, and the oversized two-car garage has enough space to keep the snow off and house a workshop.  Plus you can rest easy with the updated furnace / AC, and steel insulated roof and the low county taxes.
